member_functions.name: empty
member_functions.description: Checks if the queue is empty

member_functions.name: size
member_functions.description: Returns the number of elements in the queue

member_functions.name: front
member_functions.description: Accesses the front element of the queue

member_functions.name: back
member_functions.description: Accesses the back element of the queue

member_functions.name: push
member_functions.description: Adds an element to the back of the queue

member_functions.name: emplace
member_functions.description: Constructs an element in-place at the back of the queue

member_functions.name: pop
member_functions.description: Removes the front element from the queue

member_functions.name: swap
member_functions.description: Swaps the contents of two queues
